{"article_id":"MMiYRbVfmY7bo76E","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Romney Absorbs Boos ,","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Tells NAACP","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"That Democrats Have Failed Blacks","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"Republican presidential candidate Mitt Romney did n't expect a warm embrace","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"when he took the stage Wednesday at the NAACP annual convention in Houston .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"But the former Massachusetts governor managed to absorb sustained booing","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"after he said","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"he 'd eliminate `` Obamacare ''","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"if elected ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"and delivered a speech","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that reached out","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"- a bit -","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"to African-Americans ,","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"while remaining consistent with his conservative campaign themes .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"His pitch to members of the nation 's oldest civil rights group boiled down to this :","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"Given the economic and educational problems","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"that still beset the black community ,","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"has historic and overwhelming loyalty to the Democratic Party really paid off ?","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"`` When decades of the same promises keep producing the same failures ,","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"then it 's reasonable to rethink our approach","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"- and consider a new plan , ''","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"Romney said .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"He touted his support of charter schools and vouchers , views not unlike those of the Obama administration ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"and attempted to dismiss the notion","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"that his campaign was about helping the rich .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"`` The president wants to make this a campaign","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"about blaming the rich , ''","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"`` I want to make this a campaign","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"about helping the middle class . ''","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"The audience reaction ?","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Crickets .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"Romney did not touch the issue of voter ID laws","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"that opponents see as conservative efforts","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"to suppress the nonwhite vote .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"And Romney was careful to acknowledge President Obama 's historic election .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"But he segued into a laundry list of economic data ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"including the 14.4 percent unemployment rate in the black community ,","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"and suggested ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"if obliquely ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"that the nation 's first black president had failed them .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"`` If equal opportunity in America were an accomplished fact ,","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"then a chronically bad economy would be equally bad for everyone , ''","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"Romney said .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"`` Instead , it 's worse for African-Americans in almost every way . ''","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Romney wrapped himself in the civil rights record of his late father , Michigan Gov . George Romney ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"and closed","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"without a mention of his Mormon faith , but on a strong religious note .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"`` Every good cause on this Earth relies in the end on a plan better than ours , ''","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Romney said ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"and then quoted the Rev . Martin Luther King Jr. :","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"`` Without dependence on God ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"our efforts turn to ashes and our sunrises into darkest night . ''","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Mitt Romney tells the NAACP convention","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"he would eliminate `` Obamacare . ''","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"YouTube","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"Even the moment","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"he was booed","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"( did Romney 's speechwriters deliberately choose the freighted word `` Obamacare '' ? )","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"seemed calibrated","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"to resonate with voters outside the walls of the convention hall .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"-- Even polls","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"taken","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"after the Supreme Court upheld most of Obama 's health care law","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"show","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that at least half of Americans still oppose the legislation .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"-- His strong case for school choice ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"including a proposal","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"to have federal money `` linked to a student ,","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"so that parents can send their child to any public or charter school , or to a private school ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"where permitted , ''","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"appeals to some corners of the African-American electorate .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"But it is aimed directly at Romney 's conservative base .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"-- He slipped in a quick reference","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"to note his party-consistent opposition to same-sex marriage ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"which Obama and the NAACP have endorsed ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"but which remains an issue","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"that has caused divisions in the black community .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"`` As president , ''","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"he said , to some applause ,","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"`` I will promote strong families","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"- and I will defend traditional marriage . ''","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"-- He doubled down on his jobs message ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"including his stated aim","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"to reduce government spending","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"by eliminating `` expensive nonessential programs like Obamacare . ''","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"He cited a Chamber of Commerce members ' survey","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"( if audience eye-rolling could be heard ,","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"there would have been noise at his invocation of the powerful business network )","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"suggesting","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"that the health care law would make three-quarters of them less likely to hire people .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Peeling off African-American voters ,","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"more than 95 percent of whom voted for Obama in 2008 ,","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"has always been a long shot for Republicans","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"even without an African-American incumbent in the White House .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"Romney acknowledged that reality ,","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"but said","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"he 's not counting anybody out .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"`` I have no hidden agenda , ''","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"`` If you want a president","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"who will make things better in the African-American community ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"you are looking at him . ''","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"He left the stage a short time later , alone , and to a smattering of polite applause .","depth":4},{"id":105,"text":"In a statement after the speech , NAACP President Benjamin Todd Jealous said :","depth":5},{"id":106,"text":"`` While we are glad","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"that Governor Romney recognized the power of the black electorate ,","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"he laid out an agenda","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"that was antithetical to many of our interests .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"His criticism of the Affordable Care Act","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"- legislation","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"that will improve access to quality health care for millions -","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"signals his fundamental misunderstanding of the needs of many African Americans . ''","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"NAACP Chairman Roslyn M. Brock said of Romney :","depth":5},{"id":115,"text":"`` We appreciate","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"that he was courageous","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"and took the opportunity","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"to speak with us directly . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":237,"left":121,"right":236,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":121,"left":0,"right":120,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":120,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":236,"left":208,"right":235,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":208,"left":170,"right":207,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":170,"left":122,"right":169,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":122,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":148,"right":168,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":130,"right":147,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":125,"right":129,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":5,"right":124,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":6,"right":123,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":9,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":127,"right":13,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":127,"left":126,"right":12,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":126,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":145,"right":146,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"le